---
title: Roasted Chicken in Béarnaise Sauce with Garlic Mash and Roasted Green Beans
description: This Roasted Chicken in Béarnaise Sauce is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R10_W22_UK_QR14547-3_Main__5low-389cefcb.jpg
